{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\">&quot;Touhou Chronicle of Youkai Prayers&quot; is a 2.5D pixel roguelike action game. It tells the adventure story of Flandre Scarlet.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3295190/extras/VD_Flandre_Live.png?t=1737428719\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">In this game, you can enjoy exhilarating combat and the thrill of countering enemies. It's a game where you only need to wield a single melee weapon to experience a variety of different skills.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3295190/extras/output_a.gif?t=1737428719\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">You can trigger skills by defeating enemies or counter their abilities, which in turn generates new skills.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Whether it's the Spell Card skills triggered by defeating enemies or the countered enemy abilities, you can modify them using enhancement cards. This adds layers of depth to the gameplay, making the experience much richer.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3295190/extras/output_b.gif?t=1737428719\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Enemy melee attacks will also create a parry effect when they collide with your melee strikes, significantly enhancing the interactivity of combat.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">The game's completion mechanism is very unique. You don\u2019t have to defeat all the enemies; instead, you can strategically choose which ones to take down. This will greatly enhance your combat efficiency.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3295190/extras/output_c.gif?t=1737428719\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">The interactive elements in the scenes are quite abundant, allowing you to enjoy attacking and even destroying them with ease.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">As you progress through the game, you can unlock more functional cards, making the gameplay even more diverse and engaging.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Come join this wonderful Gensokyo for an exhilarating and thrilling adventure!</p>","background":"https://store.akamai.steamstatic.com/images/storepagebackground/app/3295190?t=1737428719","background_raw":"https://store.akamai.steamstatic.com/images/storepagebackground/app/3295190?t=1737428719","capsule_image":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3295190/f885dac8fdfdb53918e985b751643b8c569a33d6/capsule_231x87.jpg?t=1737428719","capsule_imagev5":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3295190/f885dac8fdfdb53918e985b751643b8c569a33d6/capsule_184x69.jpg?t=1737428719","categories":[{"description":"Single-player","id":2},{"description":"Multi-player","id":1},{"description":"Co-op","id":9},{"description":"Online Co-op","id":38},{"description":"LAN Co-op","id":48},{"description":"Cross-Platform Multiplayer","id":27},{"description":"Steam Achievements","id":22},{"description":"Partial Controller Support","id":18},{"description":"Steam Cloud","id":23},{"description":"Steam Leaderboards","id":25}],"content_descriptors":{"ids":[],"notes":null},"detailed_description":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\">&quot;Touhou Chronicle of Youkai Prayers&quot; is a 2.5D pixel roguelike action game. It tells the adventure story of Flandre Scarlet.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3295190/extras/VD_Flandre_Live.png?t=1737428719\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">In this game, you can enjoy exhilarating combat and the thrill of countering enemies. It's a game where you only need to wield a single melee weapon to experience a variety of different skills.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3295190/extras/output_a.gif?t=1737428719\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">You can trigger skills by defeating enemies or counter their abilities, which in turn generates new skills.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Whether it's the Spell Card skills triggered by defeating enemies or the countered enemy abilities, you can modify them using enhancement cards. This adds layers of depth to the gameplay, making the experience much richer.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3295190/extras/output_b.gif?t=1737428719\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Enemy melee attacks will also create a parry effect when they collide with your melee strikes, significantly enhancing the interactivity of combat.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">The game's completion mechanism is very unique. You don\u2019t have to defeat all the enemies; instead, you can strategically choose which ones to take down. This will greatly enhance your combat efficiency.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3295190/extras/output_c.gif?t=1737428719\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">The interactive elements in the scenes are quite abundant, allowing you to enjoy attacking and even destroying them with ease.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">As you progress through the game, you can unlock more functional cards, making the gameplay even more diverse and engaging.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Come join this wonderful Gensokyo for an exhilarating and thrilling adventure!</p>","developers":["LFCat Studio"],"genres":[{"description":"Action","id":"1"},{"description":"Adventure",